mesh well for me.

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:59.680
Generally, in this kind of app,
where you're entering

00:14:59.680 --> 00:15:04.040
data, lots of data, you probably
want to use a lighter

00:15:04.040 --> 00:15:05.050
background.

00:15:05.050 --> 00:15:07.790
I think the darker backgrounds,
like a black or

00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:11.330
the Holo dark theme, those are
best used for media apps like

00:15:11.330 --> 00:15:14.220
Gallery or playing video.

00:15:14.220 --> 00:15:18.100
And so when I'm entering text
or entering data, it seems

00:15:18.100 --> 00:15:21.070
like it's a better fit
for a lighter theme.

00:15:21.070 --> 00:15:23.470
The darker color action bar, the
blue action bar, is fine

00:15:23.470 --> 00:15:24.850
for branding.

00:15:24.850 --> 00:15:26.980
But that's just one of the first
things that jumped out.

00:15:26.980 --> 00:15:29.590
