really easy and quick to scan.

00:20:06.186 --> 00:20:06.860
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah, absolutely.

00:20:06.860 --> 00:20:08.620
NICK BUTCHER: And I think all
of these patterns as well,

00:20:08.620 --> 00:20:13.265
like one of the most important
things in this input screen as

00:20:13.265 --> 00:20:16.290
