name, where it might

00:20:33.395 --> 00:20:34.475
capitalize every letter.

00:20:34.475 --> 00:20:37.060
And I think that's really
critical for making the

00:20:37.060 --> 00:20:41.174
screens flow very fast and
making you very productive.

00:20:41.174 --> 00:20:43.070
So the developer's not
done too bad a job.

00:20:43.070 --> 00:20:45.620
